  <h1>Amoveo Exchange Instructions</h1>

  <h3> For sellers </h3>
  <ol>
  <li>Go to http://159.89.106.253:8087/main.html</li>
  <li>Deposit required VEO to exchange account (deposit address: BGDXGmovuTEr3CFfzY0xr0zXS3purkIPPZsljZv4gvQe87K6W8be1IpwDwmqhgcSIlhTvb9Q7pgrl+h2dmXGEXM= )</li>
  <li>Wait for 4 confirmations.</li>
  <li>Fill all required field:
    <ul>
    <li> bitcoin address that will receive bitcoins - Your bitcoin address </li>
  <li> address that will receive VEO - Buyer's VEO address </li>
  <li> time limit in seconds. If the bitcoin doesn't arrive within this limit, then the veo is refunded - keep it by default </li>
  <li> how many veo to sell - Amount of VEO you're selling </li>
    <li> how many bitcoin to buy - Total amount of BTC, that Buyer will send you. </li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li> Click on generate unsigned trade request </li>
  <li> Copy unsigned trade request (whole string) and sign it with light wallet http://159.65.120.84:8080/wallet.html </li>
  <li> Copy signed request from wallet and paste in into field next to publish signed trade request and click on this button. </li>
  <li> Give received trade request to buyer. </li>
  <li> Wait for the payment. </li>
  </ol>

  <h3> For buyers </h3>
  <ol>
    <li>Go to http://159.89.106.253:8087/main.html and get trade request from seller.</li>
  <li> Put that request into lookup trade field, click on the button and check all details of the deal (very carefully check your VEO address, amount of VEO and BTC) </li>
  <li> Send required BTC to seller address. </li>
  <li> Wait for 3 confirmation, after that you'll get your veo automatically(edited) </li>
  </ol>
